### Variables globales
@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000
@contentType = application/json

### Étape 1: Initialiser les données de test
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/seed
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{}

### Étape 2: Login Admin
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "email": "admin@wao.test",
  "password": "SecurePassword123!"
}

@token = eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9...

---

## PHASE 9.1 - Security & Authentication

### Test 1: Login avec credentials valides
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "email": "admin@wao.test",
  "password": "SecurePassword123!"
}

### Test 2: Login avec password invalide
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "email": "admin@wao.test",
  "password": "WrongPassword"
}

### Test 3: Route protégée sans token
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/clients
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "first_name": "John",
  "last_name": "Doe"
}

### Test 4: Route protégée avec token invalide
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/clients
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer invalid.token.here

{
  "first_name": "John",
  "last_name": "Doe"
}

### Test 5: Vérifier accès root
GET {{baseUrl}}/
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

---

## PHASE 9.2 - Business Logic

### Test 6: Créer client
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/clients
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "first_name": "Jean",
  "last_name": "Dupont",
  "email": "jean@example.com",
  "phone": "+221771234567",
  "cni": "12345678901234"
}

### Test 7: Enregistrer transaction
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/transactions
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "client_id": "client-uuid",
  "amount": 50000,
  "transaction_type": "deposit",
  "description": "Member deposit"
}

### Test 8: Enregistrer cotisation
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/cotisations
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "client_id": "client-uuid",
  "cycle_id": 1,
  "amount": 10000
}

### Test 9: Advanced Deposit
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/cotisations/advanced-deposit
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "client_id": "client-uuid",
  "cycle_id": 1,
  "cotisation_amount": 10000,
  "savings_amount": 20000
}

### Test 10: Transfer Financing to Savings
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/accounts/transfer-financing-to-savings
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "client_id": "client-uuid",
  "amount": 5000,
  "financing_account_id": "fin-account-uuid"
}

### Test 11: Invalid Client ID
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/transactions
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "client_id": "non-existent-uuid",
  "amount": 50000,
  "transaction_type": "deposit"
}

### Test 12: Negative Amount Validation
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/transactions
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "client_id": "client-uuid",
  "amount": -5000,
  "transaction_type": "deposit"
}

